name: Yellow is the magic
description:
yellow is the magic is a song cover by Lucy enigma, this song telling about how happy to have someone love, doing everything with someone love,    and all seems bright as the yellow color, like sunflower, as egg yolk and banana.

but actually, this song is made because of losing someone's love.

and, I (Anggi) have you all in this space now ♥️.

thank you for Ur support (anything)
